      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom-pristine condition, exhibiting no discernible wear to its exterior or interior surfaces. Meticulously preserved and mechanically flawless, it represents a premier acquisition for the discerning driver who demands nothing less than absolute perfection. Experience the pinnacle of its class.",
